  "texts": [
    "The first document talks about the usage of Chatbots in language learning setup, and the second document discusses the extensive use of technology in language learning.",
    "This conclusion, through bibliographic coupling, is consistent with the outcomes of the content analysis. 7.",
    "Through content analysis, we identified the most occurring textual terms used in the retrieved data from Scopus.",
    "We identified that the most occurring AI tool was Chatbots followed by Chatgpt, Conversational Agents, Automatic Speech Recognition and Intelligent Personal Assistants.",
    "We also identified the most researched language learning factor with AI which is Writing followed by Speaking, Vocabulary, Listening and Grammar."
  ]
}